section.para:
Depending if you use NixOS or other platforms you can use one of the following methods to enable sandboxing before building the package:
Globally enable sandboxing on NixOS: add the following to configuration.nix nix.useSandbox = true;
Globally enable sandboxing on non-NixOS platforms: add the following to: /etc/nix/nix.conf build-use-sandbox = true
